title: 301: Welcome to the Portal—Evolving in the Great Void with Sahara Rose
itunes:title: 301: Welcome to the Portal—Evolving in the Great Void with Sahara Rose
description:
We are in the great void right now- the space between the inhale and exhale, the womb, the cosmos, the black hole. And this is why things may feel a little weird. You used to have your footing, knowing exactly where life was “supposed” to be and now everything is totally up in the air. In this episode, I’ll be sharing with you my downloads on what is happening now from an energetic perspective. And most importantly, what we can do about it for our unique and collective optimal timelines. Let’s dive into the portal.

Being part of a conscious online community is more important than ever before. Leave your anxiety behind and get the support, connection and inspiration your soul has been craving in Rose Gold Goddesses, the sacred sisterhood all about becoming your highest self. Doors open now at rosegoldgoddesses.com

Participate in my Discover Your Dharma 10-Day Course, Healing + Embodiment Through Dance Workshop and so much more in Rose Gold Goddesses, the sacred sisterhood all about becoming your highest self. Join us today at rosegoldgoddesses.com

Intro + Outro Music: Silent Ganges by Maneesh de Moor

Discover your Dosha and receive custom results for your mind and body with my free quiz at eatfeelfresh.com/new-quiz

Connect with me for daily Ayurvedic and modern spiritual wisdom at: Instagram.com/iamsahararose
Facebook.com/iamsahararose Twitter.com/iamsahararose
